ive ion etching. A precise grating profile metrology has also been\nconducted using cleaving techniques. Finally, we show the deposit of fiducials\n(i.e. centering marks) with Aerosol Jet Printing (AJP). We conclude with the\nultimate coronagraph expected performances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Dec 2014 09:23:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-02"}
