ion wave\nin the masering medium with a gradient of radial velocities. In OH and H2O\nmasers some turbulent motions of material are inferred.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Dec 2014 13:10:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Dec 2014 12:06:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-25"}
